            "value": "### 1. [Install Nuxt](https:\/\/nuxtjs.org\/guide\/installation\/)\r\n\r\n### 2. Install the Druxt module\r\n\r\n```sh\r\nnpm i druxt\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 3. Add the module and configuration to **nuxt.config.js**:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  modules: [\r\n    'druxt'\r\n  ],\r\n  druxt: {\r\n    baseUrl: 'https:\/\/demo-api.druxtjs.org'\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```"
